review_blob: In the U.S. we are unable to get the Apt 12 but I cant imanage how good it must be because this beer the rochefort 10 is insane! It sends you to a different world with its smell and taste. not going to try to describe it in detial....just WOW!!!
Poured slowly in a pint glass (best I have), nice tan/brown color with a good head. Aroma was wounderful. Tasted great better than the double very good flavor! Lingering finish. Overall a great beer.
